                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2000-01-18</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>Once I saw the title of this book, I knew I could not pass it up. I was not disappointed! Being a weekend crafter and sewer, I like to find quick and easy ways to accent my home, clothing and gifts. It's all here in African Accents. After reading the book I learned things I did not know about the history and art of West African designs and fabrics. African Accents is a 'must read' for those interested in ethnically diverse and fun ways to decorate the home and create unique gifts and crafts.</span>
                  
              
